<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>spin control • spin out of control</xh5><p> <i>spin control—</i>manipulation of news, especially political news: The conclusion: Either we are being lied to in an effort of <u>spin control</u>, or the people in charge of our government are incompetent.</p><p> <i>spin out of control</i>—(of activities, events, etc.) change very quickly and in an uncontrolled way: The political situation in Bolivia is <u>spinning out of control</u>, and if the protests continue to intensify, they could spell serious trouble...</p> </entry>
